# Windsurf Rules for {{PROJECT_NAME}}
# These rules guide Cascade AI behavior in Windsurf IDE

## Project Context

Project: {{PROJECT_NAME}}
Type: {{PROJECT_TYPE}}  
Tech Stack: {{TECH_STACK}}

## AI Framework Integration

This project uses the Supervisor-Worker AI Framework.
- Framework location: docs/SUPERVISOR/
- Always check CURRENT-STATUS.md before major work
- Follow role protocols (SUPERVISOR or WORKER)

## Role Initialization

To initialize as SUPERVISOR:
- Read docs/SUPERVISOR/SUPERVISOR-FRAMEWORK.md
- Review CURRENT-STATUS.md and DELEGATION-TRACKER.md
- Plan and delegate tasks

To initialize as WORKER:
- Read docs/SUPERVISOR/WORKER-FRAMEWORK.md
- Find your assigned task in DELEGATION-TRACKER.md
- Execute within scope, report progress

