### Naming Conventions

{{NAMING_CONVENTIONS}}

## Testing

- Test command: {{TEST_COMMAND}}
- Write tests for new features
- Verify no regressions

## Documentation Updates

After making changes:
1. Update CHANGELOG.md (newest entries first)
2. Update README if needed
3. Update CURRENT-STATUS.md if project state changed
4. Add to DECISIONS-LOG.md if architectural decision made

## Restrictions

- Don't modify {{PROTECTED_FILES}} without explicit request
- Don't add new dependencies without justification
- Don't change established patterns without documenting why
- Don't skip handover documentation

## Session Workflow

### Starting Work
1. Read CURRENT-STATUS.md for project state
2. Check DELEGATION-TRACKER.md for active tasks
3. Initialize as appropriate role

### During Work
- Stay within assigned scope
- Report blockers immediately
- Document decisions

### Ending Session
- Update status documents
- Create handover if incomplete
- Summarize what was done

